Day 51: Execute Rolling Updates in Kubernetes

Date: October 16, 2025
Overview
Performed zero-downtime deployments using rolling updates.
Key Concepts Learned

Rolling update strategy
Deployment history
Update monitoring
Rollout status

Commands Used
bashkubectl set image deployment/nginx nginx=nginx:1.19
kubectl rollout status deployment/nginx
kubectl rollout history deployment/nginx
Challenges Faced
Understanding update strategies and ensuring applications stayed available during updates.
